It may look like an iPhone 4 but this gadget is in fact a stun gun which has landed a 21-year-old man three years in prison.

Marcel Cross was found with the concealed weapon after police were called following reports of a man with a stun gun in Bicester, Oxfordshire.

Officers who attended the scene on January 6 discovered Cross with the gun and despite his claims to have purchased it as a novelty item, he was charged with possession of a firearm.

